# English only

- Write all agent replies, commit messages, PR descriptions, and code comments in **English**.
- All user-facing UI strings (labels, errors, tooltips, alerts, disclaimers) must be in **English**.
- Do not add Russian or other localization unless the user explicitly requests it.
- Product positioning remains EN-first for EU/US (see `easyhealth.mdc`).
